<inglise> REGULATION (EEC) No 1353/75 OF THE COMMISSION of 28 May 1975 amending Regulation (EEC) No 1726/70 on the procedure for granting the premium for leaf tobacco as regards the event giving entitlement to the premium </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1353/75, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1726/70 (lehttubaka jaoks lisatasu andmise korra kohta) seoses asjaoluga, ms annab lisatasu saamise &otilde;iguse 28. mai 1975 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 727/70 (1) of 21 April 1970 on the common organization of the market in raw tobacco, as last amended by the Act (2) concerning the conditions of accession and the adjustments to the Treaties, and in particular Article 3 (3) thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 21. aprilli 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 727/70 toortubakaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud &uuml;hinemistingimusi ja asutamislepingutesse tehtavaid muudatusi k&auml;sitleva aktiga, (2) eriti selle artikli 3 l&otilde;iget 3, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, according to Article 4 (2) of Council Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68 (3) of 30 July 1968 laying down rules for the implementation of Regulation (EEC) No 653/68 (4) on conditions for alterations to the value of the unit of account used for the common agricultural policy, sums owed by a Member State or a duly authorized body, expressed in national currency and representing amounts fixed in units of account, shall be paid on the basis of the relationship between the unit of account and the national currency which obtained at the time when the transaction or part transaction was carried out; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: &uuml;hises p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitikas kasutatava arvestus&uuml;hiku v&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmistingimusi k&auml;sitleva m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 653/68 (3) rakenduseeskirju s&auml;testava n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuli 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 (4) artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 2 on s&auml;testatud, et liikmesriigi v&otilde;i selle n&otilde;uetekohaselt volitatud asutuse v&otilde;lgnetavad summad, mis on v&auml;ljendatud riigi v&auml;&auml;ringus ja esindavad arvestus&uuml;hikutes fikseeritud summasid, makstakse tehingu v&otilde;i selle osa sooritamise ajal kehtinud arvestus&uuml;hiku ja riigi v&auml;&auml;ringu vahelise suhte alusel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, according to Article 6 of the same Regulation, the time when a transaction is carried out shall be considered as being the date on which occurs the event, as defined by Community rules or, in the absence of and pending adoption of such rules, by the rules of the Member State concerned, which gives entitlement to the amount involved in the transaction; </inglise>
<eesti> nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 6 kohaselt k&auml;sitatakse tehingu sooritamise ajana kuup&auml;eva, mil ilmneb asjaolu, mis on m&auml;&auml;ratletud &uuml;henduse eeskirjades v&otilde;i nende eeskirjade puudumisel v&otilde;i kuni nende vastuv&otilde;tmiseni asjaomase liikmesriigi &otilde;igusaktides, mis annab &otilde;iguse tehinguga seotud summale; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 6 (1) of Commission Regulation (EEC) 1726/70 (5) of 25 August 1970 on the procedure for granting the premium for leaf tobacco, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 903/74 (6), stipulates that the right to the premium shall accrue as soon as the tobacco leaves the place in which it was under supervision; whereas, consequently, the amount involved in the transaction immediately becomes due and payable within the meaning of Article 6 of Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68; whereas it is therefore desirable to adopt, for the calculation of the amount of this premium in national currency, the conversion rate obtaining on the date when the tobacco leaves the place where it was under supervision; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni 25. augusti 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1726/70 (lehttubaka jaoks lisatasu andmise korra kohta, (5) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 903/74 (6)) artikli 6 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatakse, et &otilde;igus lisatasule saadakse kohe, kui lehttubakas on j&auml;relevalve alt &auml;ra viidud; seega tekib kohe m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 artiklis 6 m&auml;&auml;ratletud t&auml;henduses kohustus tasuda tehinguga seotud summa; seet&otilde;ttu tuleks lisatasu omav&auml;&auml;ringus v&auml;ljendatava summa arvutamiseks kohaldada lehttubaka j&auml;relevalve alt &auml;raviimise p&auml;eval kehtivat &uuml;mberarvestuskurssi; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinion of the Management Committee for Tobacco, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las tubakaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The following text shall be added to Article 6 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 1726/70: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1726/70 artikli 6 l&otilde;ikesse 1 lisatakse j&auml;rgmine tekst: </eesti>
<inglise> "The event giving entitlement to the premium, within the meaning of Article 6 of Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68, shall be considered to have occurred on that date. " </inglise>
<eesti> "M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 artiklis 6 m&auml;&auml;ratletud t&auml;henduses loetakse asjaolu, mis annab &otilde;iguse lisatasule, toimunuks sellel kuu&auml;eval." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 28 May 1975. </inglise>
